---
title: Goat Cheese Stuffed Chicken with Roasted Zucchini Salad
description: Chicken breasts get an upgrade with roasted red peppers and chive goat cheese! A lightly dressed salad stuffed full of roasted veggies makes this a guilt-free meal!
